Lvl 10 -> 11

Goal: The password for the next level is stored in the file data.txt, which contains base64 encoded data

Command used:

ls
cat data.txt
base64 -d data.txt

//
cat data.txt -> view content (not the password yet)
base64 -d -> Decode the base64-encoded text

##
Notice that all base64 content usually ends with '==' at the end of each line

